From January 15 until February 2:
- It is forbidden to hold meetings on the occasion of holidays, anniversaries, parties in closed and/or open, public and/or private spaces;
- Activity is prohibited in bars, clubs and discotheques, as well as in playgrounds inside shopping centers;
- It is prohibited to organize and carry out the activity in cinemas, performance institutions and/or concerts;
– It is prohibited to organize and conduct drive-in shows, as well as shows, concerts, festivals or other cultural events, held outdoors;
- Outdoor recreational and sports activities are prohibited, except for those with the participation of no more than 10 people who do not live together;
- It is prohibited to operate playgrounds, game rooms inside commercial centers where several economic operators are active;
- The activities of economic operators carried out in closed spaces in the following areas are prohibited: activities in swimming pools, playgrounds and game rooms;
- Activities with the public of licensed economic operators in the field of gambling are prohibited;
